Comment: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:53.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,出现钟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:02:03.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Fate doom and future　dark over light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:06.23,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru (get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:13.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:18.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた　shadow prison　姿潜めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:23.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,行き場を探しては　I keep my soul in you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:26.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Never give up that fight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,So break out so break out -> To battle the tension
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:33.47,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Don't let it claim your light rise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:38.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,果てなきを彷徨う　飽く無き声が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:43.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,足枷を解いて　羽ばたくの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,時間の狭間で召されてく魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,たとえ全てを焼き尽くされたとし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:53.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,ても　飲み込んで　しまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:57.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇を振り翳して　胸に宿すアンサー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.62,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1370,27)}闇中反転　照らして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:03.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1365.333,91.001)}Aren't you? 明鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:03.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0000FF&\3c&H0000FF&\3a&HFF&\pos(1370.666,35)}Won't you make yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:03.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1720,74.668)} -> 探すの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:05.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,君を守りたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,そのに呼びかけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,闇中宣戦　全身全霊　生きてゆく証
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs31\pos(1184,80)\bord1.2}climb back up unswayed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru(get out get out get out get out)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Guru-guru-guru-guru
